## Limitations

The report is based on information available from news sources as of July 2021. The situation in Cuba is dynamic, and developments may have occurred since the time of reporting. Additionally, the perspectives provided are primarily from international media, which may not fully capture the nuances of the local context and sentiments within Cuba.